Nigerian songbird, Simi is back with a new video for her song “Ayo”. The award-winning talented singer is releasing the video almost a month after she first debuted the song. The happy single has Simi distributing happiness throughout the very colourful video. Asides her vocal prowess, Simi also entertains viewers to a variety of trendy dances like the Zanku and Shaku, with assists from the casts who coloured the video with their smiles and all-around good energy. The video is directed by DK, while Legendury Beatz produced the song. Watch the video below: 